yakov fedotovich pavlov ( ; 4 october 191729 september 1981 ) was a soviet red army soldier who became a hero of the soviet union for his role in defending " pavlov 's house " during the battle of stalingrad .

world war ii in europe : sgt . yakov pavlov & a dozen russian soldiers held out for more than 50 days in the center of this city in 1942 & never lost it

